<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0006c" n="0006c"/>
<lb n="0006c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0006c02"/><head type="no">No. 1032</head>
<lb n="0006c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0006031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】卅帖策子第五，【乙】建久七年寫高山寺藏本</note>瑜伽蓮華部念誦法<note n="0006032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0006032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0006032"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0006c04"/>
<lb n="0006c05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0006033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006033" word-count="33"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0006c06"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0006c07"/>正號大廣智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0006034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大興善寺＝唐北天竺【明】</note><app n="0006034"><lem>大興善寺</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺</rdg></app>三藏沙門
<lb n="0006c08"/><note n="0006035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大廣智）＋不【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大廣智）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006035"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">大廣智不</rdg></app>空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0006c09"/><div1 type="jing"><p>初入道場。至心頂禮懺悔發願回向等已</p>
<lb n="0006c10"/><p>即結蓮華合掌印　兩手<note n="0006036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">指＝相【宋】</note><app n="0006036"><lem>指</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>虛其掌。似未開
<lb n="0006c11"/>芙蓉。誦一切法清淨真言。印心額喉頂上各
<lb n="0006c12"/>一遍。即得清淨。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0006c13"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;<note n="0006037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02124;＝戍【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006037" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><corr sic="＆CB02124；" resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB02122;</corr>＝戍【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006037"><lem>&CB02122;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">戍</rdg></app>馱薩&CB00085;達<note n="0006038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】＊</note><app n="0006038"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app><note n="0006039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑&CB00085;二合婆&CB00085;＝薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合【三】【乙】，薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合【甲】</note><note n="0006039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑&CB00085;二合婆&CB00085;＝薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，＝薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合【甲】</note><app n="0006039"><lem>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0006c14"/>婆&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">薩&CB00085;婆&CB00085;二合</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薩&CB00085;娑&CB00085;二合</rdg></app>戍度唅</p>
<lb n="0006c15"/><p>然後右膝著地。蓮華合掌置於頂上。誦真言
<lb n="0006c16"/>想禮一切諸佛菩薩本尊足。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0006c17"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>勿<note place="inline">微一<note n="0006040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】下同</note><app n="0006040"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0006c18"/><p>作此法已。即於一切諸佛菩薩。禮事供養皆
<lb n="0006c19"/>悉成就。然後結<note n="0006041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝跏【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006041"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">跏</rdg></app>趺坐或半<note n="0006042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝跏趺【明】，跏【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0006042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝跏趺【明】，＝跏【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0006042"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">跏趺</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">跏</rdg></app>坐。即結蓮
<lb n="0006c20"/>華三昧耶印。兩手外相叉合<note n="0006043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掌＝拳【乙】</note><app n="0006043"><lem>掌</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">拳</rdg></app>。&CB00594;二大指二
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0007a" n="0007a"/>
<lb n="0007a01"/>小指相並。呈示一切諸佛菩薩本尊。即憶本
<lb n="0007a02"/>誓願加持攝受。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a03"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note>三<anchor id="fxT20p0007a01"/>摩耶薩怛&CB00680;
<lb n="0007a04"/><note place="inline"><note n="0007001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【明】</note><app n="0007001"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a05"/><p>次結極喜印。准前手<note n="0007002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勢＝契【乙】</note><app n="0007002"><lem>勢</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">契</rdg></app>。但以二<note n="0007003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（手）＋中【明】</note><app n="0007003"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">手中</rdg></app>指。<note n="0007004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔垂〕－【三】</note><note n="0007004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔垂〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007004"><lem>垂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007a06"/>下於掌中。以指面相合。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a07"/><p type="dharani">唵三摩耶斛素囉多薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a08"/><p>次結開心印。觀二乳上。右<note n="0007005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛字上甲本有梵字</note>怛囉<note n="0007006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合引〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007006"><lem><note place="inline">二合<note n="0007007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【明】</note><app n="0007007"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>左<note n="0007008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒字上甲本有梵字</note>吒
<lb n="0007a09"/>字。如戶樞。以金剛縛三掣開。以開自心猶如
<lb n="0007a10"/>啟扇。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a11"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒</p>
<lb n="0007a12"/><p>次結入智印。准前金剛縛。但以二大拇指屈
<lb n="0007a13"/>入掌中。觀一肘前有白蓮花。上置<note n="0007009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡字上甲本有梵字</note>惡字字
<lb n="0007a14"/>有白光。流入心中住白蓮花上。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a15"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0007010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0007010"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>微舍<note n="0007011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝噁【明】</note><app n="0007011"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">噁</rdg></app><note n="0007012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔急〕－【三】</note><note n="0007012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔急〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007012"><lem><note place="inline">急</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0007a16"/><p>次結閉心門印。准前縛。但以<note n="0007013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【甲】</note><app n="0007013"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>頭指並<note n="0007014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝柱【乙】＊</note><app n="0007014"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">柱</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007a17"/>二大拇指節。以其印觸心。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a18"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0007a02"/>引</note>母瑟知&CB00805;<note place="inline">即觀門閉</note></p>
<lb n="0007a19"/><p>次結定印。兩手相叉仰安臍下。以二大拇指
<lb n="0007a20"/>向上相捻。即誦入三摩地真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007a21"/><p type="dharani">唵三摩地&CB00425;娜<note n="0007015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彌＝弭【明】</note><app n="0007015"><lem>彌</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">弭</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007a22"/><p>次應端身正念入三摩地。舌<anchor id="fxT20p0007a03"/>拄上&CB00171;止諸攀
<lb n="0007a23"/>緣。觀內外一切法皆無所有。若妄念多者應
<lb n="0007a24"/>先數息。數息法從一息至七息。又從一至七
<lb n="0007a25"/>相續不絕。心無攀緣即不須數息。深入清淨
<lb n="0007a26"/>無所有處。即觀諸佛遍滿虛空。其身大小猶
<lb n="0007a27"/>如胡麻具諸相好。告行者言。善男子汝觀自
<lb n="0007a28"/>心。又觀己身遍禮佛足。白佛言世尊云何觀
<lb n="0007a29"/>心。心何相貌。諸佛告言。善男子心相難可測
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0007b" n="0007b"/>
<lb n="0007b01"/>量。授與真言密誦觀察。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007b02"/><p type="dharani">唵質多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底微鄧迦嚕弭</p>
<lb n="0007b03"/><p>行者密誦諦觀己心猶如淨月。諸佛告言。善
<lb n="0007b04"/>男子汝心本如是。<note n="0007016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">但＝怛【宋】【元】</note><app n="0007016"><lem>但</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">怛</rdg></app>客塵所翳。當知此即是
<lb n="0007b05"/>菩提心。又授真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007b06"/><p type="dharani">唵冒地質多　<note n="0007017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畝＝母【明】</note><app n="0007017"><lem>畝</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">母</rdg></app>怛波<note place="inline">二合</note>娜夜弭</p>
<lb n="0007b07"/><p>誦此真言。諦觀心月<note n="0007018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉＝輪【乙】</note><app n="0007018"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">輪</rdg></app>更分明淨無瑕翳。即
<lb n="0007b08"/>於月輪中觀紇<note n="0007019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唎＝哩【明】</note><app n="0007019"><lem>唎</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>字。成<note n="0007020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝百【宋】【元】</note><app n="0007020"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">百</rdg></app>八葉白蓮花
<lb n="0007b09"/>光明顯照。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007b10"/><p type="dharani">唵底瑟<note n="0007021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00109;＝吒【明】＊</note><app n="0007021"><lem>&CB00109;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">吒</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b11"/><p>次又觀此白蓮華遍周法界量同虛空。真言
<lb n="0007b12"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0007b13"/><p type="dharani">唵薩癹<note place="inline">二合</note>囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0007b01"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b14"/><p>次觀白蓮華漸漸收斂。虛空諸佛悉入其中
<lb n="0007b15"/>量等己身。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007b16"/><p type="dharani">唵僧<note n="0007022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀【明】</note><app n="0007022"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app>囉&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0007b02"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007b17"/><p>即變蓮華成觀自在菩薩。寶冠瓔珞相好莊嚴。
<lb n="0007b18"/>放大光明遍周法界。冠上有無量壽佛本尊
<lb n="0007b19"/>左手執白蓮花。右手作擘開蓮華勢。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007b20"/><p type="dharani">唵三摩喻<note n="0007023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">含＝舍【甲】</note><app n="0007023"><lem>含</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">舍</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT20p0007b03"/>摩訶三摩喻含薩婆怛<note n="0007024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他孽＝多孽【明】，他&CB00617;【乙】</note><note n="0007024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他孽＝多孽【明】，＝他&CB00617;【乙】</note><app n="0007024"><lem>他孽</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">多孽</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">他&CB00617;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0007b21"/><note n="0007025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝多引【宋】【元】，哆【明】</note><note n="0007025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多＝多引【宋】【元】，＝哆【明】</note><app n="0007025"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">多引</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app>毘三冒地&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0007026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【三】</note><note n="0007026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝麼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007026"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>阿怛
<lb n="0007b22"/><anchor id="fxT20p0007b04"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note>句含</p>
<lb n="0007b23"/><p>入是三昧者。一切天龍八部。見行者身與觀
<lb n="0007b24"/>自在等無差別。能除行者無量億劫生死重
<lb n="0007b25"/>罪。一切勝願無不悉<note n="0007027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地＝成【宋】【元】，備【明】</note><note n="0007027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地＝成【宋】【元】，＝備【明】</note><app n="0007027"><lem>地</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">備</rdg></app>。現得圓滿金剛法
<lb n="0007b26"/>身。即觀此身便成正覺</p>
<lb n="0007b27"/><p>次結加持印。外相叉金剛<note n="0007028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛結＝結縛【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0007028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛結＝結縛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007028"><lem>縛結</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">結縛</rdg></app>已。即變屈二
<lb n="0007b28"/>頭指。捻二大拇指。印心額喉頂各誦一遍。真
<lb n="0007b29"/>言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0007c" n="0007c"/>
<lb n="0007c01"/><p type="dharani">唵紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note>薩婆迦哩阿地瑟<anchor id="fxT20p0007c01"/>&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0007c02"/>合</note>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0007c03"/><p>次結灌頂印。合掌已。&CB00594;二大拇指。偃<note n="0007029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蹙＝戚【乙】</note><app n="0007029"><lem>蹙</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">戚</rdg></app>八
<lb n="0007c04"/>指如寶形。置於頂上誦真言三遍。想五如來
<lb n="0007c05"/>冠以冠其首。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007c06"/><p type="dharani">唵紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note>摩抳&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0007c02"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note>阿毘詵者薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0007c07"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;怛<note n="0007030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【三】【甲】，洛【乙】</note><note n="0007030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，＝洛【乙】</note><app n="0007030"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB02255;</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">洛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007c08"/><p>次結繫鬘印誦真言。以前冠頂印。從<note n="0007031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">額＝頭【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007031"><lem>額</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">頭</rdg></app>分
<lb n="0007c09"/>二手。於腦後三相繞如繫鬘。便向前耳邊下。
<lb n="0007c10"/>從小指散垂如鬘帶勢。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007c11"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0007c03"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0007032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【明】</note><app n="0007032"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>隸&CB00805;紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0007c12"/><p>次結甲冑印。結金剛拳如小兒握固。以二頭
<lb n="0007c13"/>指各<anchor id="fxT20p0007c04"/>拄二大拇指節。當心已。即伸二頭指相
<lb n="0007c14"/>掩一節許。仍以右<note n="0007033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">指＋（押）【三】</note><note n="0007033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">指＋（押）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007033"><lem>指</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">指押</rdg></app>左指上。觀右頭指面有
<lb n="0007c15"/>唵字。左頭指面有<note n="0007034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跕＝砧【三】</note><note n="0007034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跕＝砧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0007034"><lem>跕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">砧</rdg></app>字。口中仍誦此兩字真
<lb n="0007c16"/>言不斷絕。想其字並放綠色光。如抽藕絲光
<lb n="0007c17"/>不斷絕。心前三繞。<note n="0007035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔背上三繞〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007035"><lem>背上三繞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。又至臍又至
<lb n="0007c18"/>兩膝。又至腰又當心。次右肩左肩次至額上。
<lb n="0007c19"/>又於腦後各<note n="0007036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＋（遍）【明】</note><app n="0007036"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">三遍</rdg></app>繞已。&CB00230;結金剛拳印從小指
<lb n="0007c20"/>散如垂天衣</p>
<lb n="0007c21"/><p>即以二縛不得解。但以掌三相拍。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007c22"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0007c05"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note n="0007037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">史＝使【明】</note><app n="0007037"><lem>史</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>也<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0007038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斛＋（引）細註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0007038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斛＋（引）細註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007038"><lem>斛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">斛<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0007c23"/><p>次於壇中觀阿<note n="0007039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】，〔上〕－【甲】</note><app n="0007039"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">上聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字成月輪。於月輪中觀紇
<lb n="0007c24"/>唎<note n="0007040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007040"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>字成本尊身。放大光明。無量眷屬普
<lb n="0007c25"/>現於圓光內</p>
<lb n="0007c26"/><p>即結鉤印。金剛縛舉右頭指。如鉤三招。一誦
<lb n="0007c27"/>一招。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0007c28"/><p type="dharani">唵阿夜係弱</p>
<lb n="0007c29"/><p><note n="0007041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＋（結）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0007041"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">次結</rdg></app>以索印。如前縛以二頭指相<anchor id="fxT20p0007c06"/>拄如環。引
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0008a" n="0008a"/>
<lb n="0008a01"/>本尊入所觀智身。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a02"/><p type="dharani">唵阿係吽吽</p>
<lb n="0008a03"/><p>次結鎖印。准前縛以二頭指及二<note n="0008001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0008001"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>指。相串
<lb n="0008a04"/>各相捻如聯鎖。令本尊止住。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a05"/><p type="dharani">唵係薩普<note n="0008002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合吒&CB00805;＝吒二合&CB00680;【三】，吒三合&CB00805;【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合吒&CB00805;＝吒二合&CB00680;【宋】【元】【明】，＝吒三合&CB00805;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008002"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note>吒&CB00805;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">吒二合&CB00680;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吒三合&CB00805;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0008a06"/><p>次結鈴印。准前縛屈二大拇指入掌中。三撼
<lb n="0008a07"/>手如搖鈴。令本尊歡喜。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a08"/><p type="dharani">唵尾舍耶斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0008a09"/><p>次結獻<note n="0008003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遏＝閼【明】</note><app n="0008003"><lem>遏</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">閼</rdg></app>伽香水印。誦百字真言或餘讚歎。
<lb n="0008a10"/>兩手外相叉擘開掌。以二中指頭相合。以二
<lb n="0008a11"/>頭指微屈。去中指<note n="0008004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔背〕－【三】</note><note n="0008004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔背〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0008004"><lem>背</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一麥許不相著。狀如
<lb n="0008a12"/>三鈷杵頭。二大拇指博著二頭指下側。即想
<lb n="0008a13"/>香水滿掬。誦真言向前寫灌洗本尊足。真言
<lb n="0008a14"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0008a15"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日<note n="0008005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00080;＝路【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0008005"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">路</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>娜迦<note n="0008006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坼＝吒【明】</note><app n="0008006"><lem>坼</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">吒</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0008a16"/><p>本尊既至次結羯<note n="0008007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝磨【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝磨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008007"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app>印。左手金剛拳當心著。
<lb n="0008a17"/>想把白蓮華。右手亦金剛拳於上轉。想撥開
<lb n="0008a18"/>蓮<note n="0008008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">葉＝華【三】</note><note n="0008008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉＝華【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0008008"><lem>葉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">華</rdg></app>即身。同本尊事業真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a19"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達<anchor id="fxT20p0008a01"/>摩紇唎<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0008a20"/><p>次結三昧耶印。金剛縛屈二頭指。以二大拇
<lb n="0008a21"/>指押。同已上加持印。令本尊憶<note n="0008009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本＋（尊）【乙】</note><app n="0008009"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">本尊</rdg></app>誓願加持
<lb n="0008a22"/>攝護。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a23"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;迦<note n="0008010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">里＝哩【明】</note><app n="0008010"><lem>里</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0008011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦三遍＝三遍誦【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008011"><lem>誦三遍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">三遍誦</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0008a24"/><p>然後結金剛嬉戲內供養印。金剛縛伸二大
<lb n="0008a25"/>拇指。偃向身相並當心。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a26"/><p type="dharani">唵摩訶囉底<note place="inline">丁以反</note></p>
<lb n="0008a27"/><p>次結鬘。准前印更不改。但以二<note n="0008012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臂＝擘【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008012"><lem>臂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">擘</rdg></app>相並直
<lb n="0008a28"/>伸。向前當額。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008a29"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0008013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00080;＝&CB02255;【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008013"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB02255;</rdg></app>波輸<note n="0008014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陛＝階【甲】</note><app n="0008014"><lem>陛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">階</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0008b" n="0008b"/>
<lb n="0008b01"/><p>次結歌印。不改前印。從前至口解散。向前垂
<lb n="0008b02"/>二手下。如發歌音。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008b03"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB02122;<note n="0008015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧＝&CB02828;【甲】</note><app n="0008015"><lem>嚧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB02828;</rdg></app><note place="inline">上輸律反下縷音二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>燥溪</p>
<lb n="0008b04"/><p>次結舞印。以二金剛拳相旋繞。各從小指散。
<lb n="0008b05"/>便金剛合掌置於頂上<note place="inline">金剛合掌者合掌令指頭右押左頭相交<note n="0008016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是也〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008016"><lem>是也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>真
<lb n="0008b06"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0008b07"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;布<note n="0008017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝逝【明】</note><app n="0008017"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">逝</rdg></app><note place="inline">而曳反</note>　已上<note n="0008018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內四＝四內【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內四＝四內【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008018"><lem>內四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">四內</rdg></app>供養</p>
<lb n="0008b08"/><p>次結焚香印。以金剛縛向下<note n="0008019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解散＝散解【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008019"><lem>解散</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">散解</rdg></app>。如焚香。
<lb n="0008b09"/>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008b10"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>訶囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;寧<note place="inline"><note n="0008020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】</note><app n="0008020"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app>引</note></p>
<lb n="0008b11"/><p>次結華印。以金剛縛向上解散。如散華。真言
<lb n="0008b12"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0008b13"/><p type="dharani">唵頗&CB00256;&CB00344;弭</p>
<lb n="0008b14"/><p>次結燈印。准前嬉戲。但以二大拇指。頭屈前
<lb n="0008b15"/>相逼。亦不得相著指。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008b16"/><p type="dharani">唵素帝惹<note n="0008021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仡＝紇【乙】</note><app n="0008021"><lem>仡</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">紇</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0008b17"/><p>次結塗香印。以金剛縛解散。摩胸上如塗香
<lb n="0008b18"/>勢真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008b19"/><p type="dharani">唵素<note n="0008022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巘＝&CB03306;【宋】【元】，喭【明】</note><note n="0008022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巘＝&CB03306;【宋】【元】，＝喭【明】</note><app n="0008022"><lem>巘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB03306;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">喭</rdg></app>蕩儗<note place="inline">妍以反</note>　已上外四供養</p>
<lb n="0008b20"/><p>次結部心根本印。合掌以二<note n="0008023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008023"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>名指二頭指。
<lb n="0008b21"/>初分相交。其二小指二大拇指擘開。誦百字
<lb n="0008b22"/>真言三遍。三字半七遍已於頂上散。然後
<lb n="0008b23"/>執念珠念誦。二手把珠當心念誦。諦觀本
<lb n="0008b24"/>尊放淨光明。流注已頂照於心月。月有白
<lb n="0008b25"/>蓮華。身與本尊色相無二。如<note n="0008024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝有【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008024"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>明鏡自觀
<lb n="0008b26"/>己身。與本尊互成影像。遍數終<note n="0008025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訖＝說【甲】</note><app n="0008025"><lem>訖</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>懺悔發
<lb n="0008b27"/>願。重獻三昧耶重結八供養。然後發遣聖者
<lb n="0008b28"/>復還本宮。發遣者用前三昧耶印當口解。真
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1032.0008c" n="0008c"/>
<lb n="0008c01"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0008c02"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;娜<anchor id="fxT20p0008c01"/>摩<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛<note n="0008026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0008026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛＝&CB00085;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0008026"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>穆<note place="inline"><note n="0008027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輕＋（呼）【明】</note><app n="0008027"><lem>輕</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">輕呼</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0008c03"/><p>然後<note n="0008028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【甲】</note><app n="0008028"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>結加持灌頂甲冑拍印等。然後出道
<lb n="0008c04"/>場。或讀大乘經。或印佛作塔。於一切時本尊
<lb n="0008c05"/>三<note n="0008029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【乙】</note><app n="0008029"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>地不令間斷。若觸穢處當觀頂上有法
<lb n="0008c06"/>界生字。<note n="0008030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">放＝於【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008030"><lem>放</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>赤色光。所謂&CB00771;字。於所食物皆
<lb n="0008c07"/>加持此字。即不成穢觸於一切供養香華。皆
<lb n="0008c08"/>加<note n="0008031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008031"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>此字放白色光。即無穢觸。所供養物
<lb n="0008c09"/>皆遍法界</p>
<lb n="0008c10"/><p>蓮華<note n="0008032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔部〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0008032"><lem>部</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>百字真言曰</p>
<lb n="0008c11"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0008033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】，磨【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩＝麼【明】，＝磨【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008033"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0008034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔下同〕－【明】＊</note><app n="0008034"><lem>下同</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT20p0008c02"/>下同</note>三<note n="0008035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩耶二摩努＝麼耶三麼弩【宋】，麼耶二麼弩【元】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0008035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩耶二摩努＝麼耶三麼弩【宋】，＝麼耶二麼弩【元】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0008035"><lem>摩耶<note place="inline">二</note><anchor id="fxT20p0008c03"/>摩
