<lb n="0008c15"/>素補使諭<anchor id="fxT20p0008c05"/><note place="inline">二合</note><anchor id="fxT20p0008c06"/>寐婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">九</note>薩&CB00085;悉地寐&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0008c16"/>合</note>也<note n="0008040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑳＝縒【明】</note><app n="0008040"><lem>瑳</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">縒</rdg></app><note place="inline">十</note>薩&CB00085;羯磨素者<anchor id="fxT20p0008c07"/>寐<note place="inline">十一</note>質多室唎<note place="inline">二
